<div style="color:#4B4B4B;">	
Here are the options for lodging:<br><br>

1. The SEARCA hotel (within the university campus)<br><br>

2. The CEC (Continuing Education Center) dorm (also within the university campus)<br><br>

3. Private lodging houses in the Los Baños town area. Use Google to identify these.<br><br>

You should make your own lodging arrangements. Reach out to these facilities by telephone or email.<br><br>


Makati Aikido Club member Mel Camus is this year's designated lodging coordinator for MAC members. If you have questions, he'll be happy to answer them even if you're not a Makati Aikido Club member. Please email him at <a href="mailto:melchizedekcamus@gmail.com">melchizedekcamus@gmail.com</a>.<br><br>

